            <ol>
                <li>You have stated your date of birth as <strong><apex:outputText value="{0, date, MMMM d, yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!candidate.Date_Of_Birth__c}" /></apex:outputText></strong> and this has been recorded by the Company as the authenticated date of birth for all purposes. No change in the same will be permitted, under any circumstances, throughout your service with the Company.</li>
                
                <li>Your base location shall be Chennai and your place of work will be at our office at Plot No. 4B1, KSR Nagar Main Road, KSR Nagar, Ambattur, Chennai – 600 053.</li>
                
